            <title>[SOLR-253] Add a RequiredWordFilter that acts like the inverse of a StopFilter</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SOLR-253</link>
                <project id="12310230" key="SOLR">Solr</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Add a filter factory that only keeps tokens with text in the required word list.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt; &amp;lt;filter class=&quot;solr.RequiredWordFilterFactory&quot; ignoreCase=&quot;true&quot; words=&quot;requiredwords.txt&quot;  /&amp;gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
